OL,3,CMan, 28, who died on street named
OL,5,FA man who died on a street in in
OL,6,FLeicester has been named by police as
OL,7,FErvin Lita.
OL,9,FThe 28-year-old was found by East
OL,10,FMidlands Ambulance Service in Compton
OL,11,FRoad in the early hours of Sunday, 12
OL,12,FJuly. He was pronounced dead at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FTwo men, aged 36 and 27, both from
OL,16,FLeicester, have been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murder in connection with
OL,18,Fthe investigation.
OL,20,FThey have both since been released on
OL,21,Fpolice bail while enquiries continue.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
