OL,3,CMan, 28, who died on street named
OL,5,FLeicestershire Police said: "An
OL,6,Finvestigation remains ongoing as we
OL,7,Fcontinue to establish how Ervin came
OL,8,Fto be in the street and the full
OL,9,Fcircumstances of what has happened.
OL,11,F"Ervin's next of kin continue to be
OL,12,Fsupported by trained officers as the
OL,13,Finvestigation remains ongoing."
OL,15,FForensic officers were seen working at
OL,16,Fthe scene on Sunday, with a blue
OL,17,Fpolice tent erected within the cordon
OL,18,Fearlier that morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
