OL,3,CMan, 28, who died on street named
OL,5,FDetective Inspector Kevin Hames, from
OL,6,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,7,FUnit, said: "Our investigation very
OL,8,Fmuch remains ongoing.
OL,10,F"We have a dedicated team progressing
OL,11,Fa number of enquiries as we continue
OL,12,Fto establish the full circumstances of
OL,13,Fwhat has happened. This includes CCTV
OL,14,Fanalysis, forensic examination and
OL,15,Fspeaking with witnesses.
OL,17,F"I continue to ask that anyone with
OL,18,Fany information, who has not yet
OL,19,Fspoken with us, does make contact with
OL,20,Fus as soon as possible.
OL,26,@oD@MOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
